snippet.title: RED BARON II TRAILER 1997 (HD)
snippet.description:
Watch in High Definition (HD) for best quality by clicking "Watch in HD" below the video.

Red Baron II is a computer game for the PC, developed by Dynamix and published by Sierra Entertainment. It is the follow up to the immensely successful flight simulation Red Baron, released in 1990.

References
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Red_Baron_II
